headline: WEC Energy Group's Corporate Responsibility Report highlights sustainable progress for an enduring enterprise
summary: WEC Energy Group (NYSE: WEC) today released its 2024 Corporate Responsibility Report. The report outlines the progress made by WEC Energy Group's family of companies on major projects and the company's mission to deliver affordable, reliable and clean energy across the Midwest.
